entries.journal_entry_description: You're doing some crafting for Gendra.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Gendra's friend is fighting with his spiced tea distributor, so you're going to help him out in the interim. You need to make him 10 spiced teas.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Now that you've crafted some spiced tea you should take it to Gendra's friend, the bartender Muna Skish. You can find him near the cantina.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: You should return to see Gendra.
